  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4be8d2e7c5845e2ce66c0f7eec192d6d.poster.avif?t=1638101660\" width=600 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4be8d2e7c5845e2ce66c0f7eec192d6d.webm?t=1638101660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4be8d2e7c5845e2ce66c0f7eec192d6d.mp4?t=1638101660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>EscapeVr </strong>is a fantastic adventure with unique gameplay, where<strong> exploration, action and research</strong> mix into an extraordinary experience that tests the limits of your performance.<br><br>Feel the evil in the darkness of a scary apartment and find a way out before the police arrive and find you together with a dead body.<br><br><strong>Everything you find in this world is designed for absolute realism, so think logically ...</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Play EscapeVr and use your extraordinary skills to advance in adventure. <br></li><li>Investigate an abandoned apartment for clues and suspects. <br></li><li><strong>Absolutely realistic environment.</strong></li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4dabe41b65a7cf238af6e1bc2ba1aab7.poster.avif?t=1638101660\" width=600 height=468 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4dabe41b65a7cf238af6e1bc2ba1aab7.webm?t=1638101660\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1350170/extras/4dabe41b65a7cf238af6e1bc2ba1aab7.mp4?t=1638101660\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
